Package civitas.celestis.util.tuple

Interface LongTuple

All Superinterfaces:
BaseTuple<Long>, Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
Long1, Long2, Long3, Long4, LongArrayTuple
public interface LongTuple extends BaseTuple<Long>
A specialized tuple which holds the primitive type long. Long tuples can be converted to their boxed form by calling boxed().
